Commented on #76 Every other request to /v1/users returns 503

Thanks for the question, it might be unclear that how those changes fixed it but it was updating packages and making the configuration correct for rabbitmq. Before it just sent the event to the main-queue but after the changes it sends it for example to users-queue because other services were picking up the request to users, so users service would not receive it, it couldn't respond. TLDR; the data fetching request didnt go to the right destination all the time
